by the great thinkers. . .

08:16.412 --> 08:19.961
. . .like Kierkegaard and Plato.
Some kids chose the Bible.

08:20.692 --> 08:23.570
I did my paper on
Harold and the Purple Crayon.

08:24.052 --> 08:26.122
It's a small book
about a little boy. . .

08:26.372 --> 08:29.170
. . .who draws the world
the way he wants it to be. . .

08:29.372 --> 08:31.010
. . .with his magic crayon.

08:31.452 --> 08:34.602
